{
  "name": "Bloody Roar",
  "type": "feat",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>At 3rd level, your satisfaction at ending an foe strikes fear into the hearts of others. If your unarmed strike reduces a creature to 0 hit points or scores a critical hit, you can use a bonus action to unleash a terrifying roar. Every creature of your choice within 30 feet of you that can hear or see you must make a Wisdom saving throw (DC equal to 8 + your proficiency bonus + your Strength modifier). On a failed save, a creature is frightened of you until the end of your next turn.</p>",
